			<div class="content" id="post-content-2308930">
									

<p>What is anomalous, anyway?</p>
<p>We tell stories about all sorts of things that just plain shouldn't be, but oddly are. However, sometimes, truth is stranger than fiction. Sometimes, the real world starts serving up things that push the boundary of reality for us. What have you encountered? Post about it here!</p>
<p>I'll start with <a href="http://www.nature.com/news/military-technology-laser-weapons-get-real-1.17613" target="_blank">this article in Nature</a> about recent developments in laser weapon technology. Yes, it's real. But an actual invisible, silent beam that can take out threats at distance? Kinda spooky.</p>

							</div>

								
